 2020-03922020-05-25,  ,  ,  ,  NRCAN
ActCanadian Energy Regulator Act
PrecisApproval of the designation by the Minister of Natural Resources of SANDRA DIANE LAPOINTE of Calgary, Alberta, to be acting Chief Executive Officer of the Canadian Energy Regulator, to hold office during pleasure for a term of six months, or until such time as a new Chief Executive Officer is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective June 1, 2020.
